body.name: SEDETA 63" Computer Desk, Office Desk with Lock Drawers for Legal/Letter File, Gaming Desk with LED Light & Power Outlet, Home Office Desks for Printer, Rustic Brown
features: 【What can you get?】 Computer desk comes with file drawer for Legal/Letter/A4 size files, small lockable drawer, power outlet, LED light, keyboard tray, printer storage space, extra long monitor stand that can hold 3 monitors, 2 storage shelves and CPU stand. An ideal office desk for small rooms to create excellent home office space.

【Multifunctional】Home office desks equipped with 4 AC outlets and 2 PowerIQ-enabled USB charging ports with switch to provide power for up to 6 devices simultaneously. The monitor stand can easily raise the monitor to a suitable height, reducing the tension and pain of the back and neck. The keyboard tray is ideal for 108-key or 87-key keyboard + mouse, which can free up more desktop space. CPU stand protects the host from moisture and dust.

【Ample Storage Space】Desk is coming with a file drawer, lockable small drawer, printer cabinet and 2 tier storage shelves, with powerful storage space. File drawer can hold Letter/Legal/A4 size files. Lockable drawer can help you privately and efficiently storage supplies. This solid constructed computer desk could hold printers and any other office machines, keeps printer or scanner within easy reach of your desk to free up work space, saving the budget for an printer stand.

【Cool & Smart LED Light Strips 】The SEDETA gaming desk comes with an RGB LED light strip, remote control via APP, Multiple Colors, and 29 flashing modes for you to choose from. LED light strip with music sync function, built-in sensitivity adjustable mic, led light color will change with the rhythm of the sound and music. With the timer function, just enjoy it in a smart way, and create a gaming and working atmosphere. Light up your gaming desk with an LED light strip.

【Easy Assemble & After-sales Service】To make assembling this sturdy office desk as effortless as possible, we have included clear and detailed instructions, numbered parts. If your item arrives damaged, scratched or missing part, please feel free to contact us, we will send you free replacement or offer a partial refund.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Create a productive, simple work or gaming space with SEDETA computer desk.

Power Strip with Switch & Monitor Stand The power outlet with switch is designed to cut off the flow of electricity to your unit, assuring that your unit is safe from overheating.Our charging station includes 4-Outlet & 2 USB Ports to provide power for up to 6 devices simultaneously. Use this computer monitor riser to easily raise your monitor to just the right height, reducing back and neck strain and pain.

Desk with File Cabinet The office desk comes with a file drawer, printer cabinet, and one open storage shelf, with powerful storage space. File cabinet can hold legal/letter/A4-size files, and is ideal for important/confidential documents, keep them organized and safely tucked away.

Desk with Lock Drawer A lockable drawer(drawer size: 16 "L x 14.6" W x 6.7 "H) can help you get rid of a messy desk and keep your workspace neat. Large Surface The L-shaped computer desk could hold three desktop computers and one notebook computer. Desktop Dimension: 63"L x 19.7" W

CPU stand & Hook CPU stand protects the host from moisture and dust. The hook is suitable for bags or headphones. Cable Management Grommets Cables management grommets provide a reasonable layout and make your desk perfectly organized.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 11, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good budget desk
reviews.reviewText: Perfectly adequate for the price. Everything went together nicely with no manufaturing defects or blemishes. The drawers open and close nicely, and the veneer seems relatively durable.If you have a larger tower case, you will likely need to remove the "middle shelf" on the right side, but this is very easily done even after the desk is fully built.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 10, 2024
reviews.reviewText: The desk is great size and fits my needs. All the parts were a little intimidating, but this 70 year old grandma can do anything. Took me most of the day to put it together, would have been easier with 2 people. If I do any more of these I will get hex wrench drill bits too.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 6, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Great end result
reviews.reviewText: The final result was a desk with every feature I was looking for that seems very sturdy. The style is also nice. I am happy I ended up with the pull out key board shelf, the file drawer, the extra shelves. there's plenty of room for storage for sure. Baskets fit nicely on the shelves to store items without visual clutter.The end result was that everything went together exactly as expected with no disappointment with how it functions.My one and only complaint is that it took the better part of a day for my husband and I to put together. The pictures in the instructions are very hard to see detail.... and believe me, you will have to pay very close attention to detail. there are very few words... mostly pictures and they either don't show detail or are too small to see what you need to. The pictures focus in on the exact part but don't show the bigger context. We got one cross bar installed with the holes facing the wrong direction and had to take it half apart again.And the absolutely worst part was figuring out how the bracets attach for the pull out key board shelf. it was very confusing. Absolutely not one single thing comes pre-set/assembled. you will be installing every last bracket and piece of hardware.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 6, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Surprisingly good quality for the price.
reviews.reviewText: I’m impressed! The desk is very sturdy and the desktop is quite durable and easy to clean. Simple to assemble. Would 100% buy again.The light strips were a little disappointing, but honestly, that wasn’t a make or break factor.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 10, 2024
reviews.reviewText: The build was pretty easy but too awhile. Pay attention to the instructions. The pictures show you where the holes need to line up. Don’t fully tighten everything until the end bc some steps need room to slide into place before you fully tighten the screws. Install the power source before you install the top shelf. Assembly took me about 3 hours. It does show fingerprints easily but they wipe away with some surface cleaner.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 10, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Excellent piece, sturdy, plenty of room, outlets and attractive.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 3, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I am very happy with this product. Metal frame, nice coloring on both sides of every piece of wood. Just two main types of screws. Easy assembly, pay attention to the pictures and follow the directions. You shouldn’t have any issues. I assembled it by myself and it took about 90 minutes. Highly recommend. Don.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 6, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Overall Acceptable and good value for the price
reviews.reviewText: It is sturdy once assembled and very spacious desktop, easily fits 3 large monitors on the top level leaving all of the desktop surface space as work area. It took 2 people 2 hours to assemble because there are so many parts, but it went together smoothly and we followed previous feedback to not tighten everything down until assembled to ensure better alignment of parts. We had to repair the main desk wood surface, the corner was cracked (not broken off), filled with wood glue and put some finishing nails into it. The cracked part is at the back middle, so cosmetically it cannot be seen. One of the assembly pieces broke when torque was applied. One screw as defective and could not be used. One leg had a dent in it, again on the back side.
